Node "Kelly_8"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Fire away, mister."
 NPCFemaleText "Fire away, sister."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's Jedrek like to work for?" linkto "Kelly_4_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who else works for Jedrek?" linkto "Kelly_5_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about the route your caravan takes?" linkto "Kelly_6_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Kelly, I've been speaking to Alexander and I need to talk to you about something." linkto "Kelly_7_1"  notes "This option only comes up if the player has spoken to Alexander about Jedrek's prices AND Kelly has NOT said node Kelly_7_2Na_4, where Kelly agrees to speak to Jedrek about his prices.\n\nIF Kelly has spoken node Kelly_7_2B_1, where the PC has told Kelly that Alexander said some very rude things about her, go to Kelly_7_2B_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think it's time you had that conversation with Jedrek about his prices." linkto "Kelly_7_2Na_4"  notes "This node only comes up IF Kelly has said node Kelly_7_4, where Kelly agrees to speak to Jedrek about his prices."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Come to think of it, I've got better things to do than waste my time listening to your bullshit." linkto "Kelly_9_1"  notes ""
